name: Planet Memes Coin (PMC)
description: Planet Memes Studio is a pioneering web3 gaming platform that creates unique and engaging gaming experiences by integrating memes, NFTs, and blockchain technology. With a focus on real-time strategy (RTS) and match-3 games, Planet Memes Studio seeks to transform the gaming industry by blending traditional gameplay elements with the exciting possibilities of web3. Built by a team of experienced game developers and blockchain experts, Planet Memes Studio offers a sustainable and enjoyable gaming ecosystem for gamers and meme enthusiasts alike.
